sources.title: Warbirds | Full Movie | Action Adventure | Brian Krause | Shauna Rappold
sources.description:
*Warbirds* - At the end of World War II, a band of Women's Air Service Corps are enlisted to ferry a top-secret weapon to an American airbase. However, they run into a violent storm and are stranded on a tiny deserted island. The crew encounters Japanese soldiers led by Captain Ozu, and more terrifyingly, Pterodons, flying monsters that have devastated Ozu's command.
2008. Stars: Jamie Elle Mann, Brian Krause, Tohoru Masamune

metadata.Plot: During WWII, a pilot and her crew carry a small group of American soldiers and an unknown cargo. However they get caught in a storm and they are forced to land in what is thought to be enemy territory. But the small island they land on holds more than men with guns.
metadata.Writer: Kevin Gendreau, Christian McIntire, John Terlesky
metadata.Actors: Jamie Elle Mann, Brian Krause, Tohoru Masamune
